name: My Window #1
description:
Well, It´s a pleasure to start this collection "Every day I feel different" about my window, my feelings, and my life.

I have been traveling as I said in my others objkts
But since I raised again in Buenos Aires
I needed to search sense in my quotidian

Travel is awesome when you realize that every day is really different
But stop traveling and being in only one place sedentary, it may seem to be all the same.
Being in only one place after all started to be a challenge for me.
Travel was my comfort zone, so I just realize what I had to do.
